            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>Heron Road Community Centre and <a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/recreation-facilities/facility-listing/heron-seniors-centre#">Heron Seniors' Centre</a> are located in the heart of the community. We offer a wide selection of recreational activities for preschoolers to older adults with dance classes, piano lessons, summer camps, sports, martial arts and fitness classes. Our centre features a full gymnasium, weight and cardio room, several multi-purpose rooms, a kitchen, a state-of-the-art theatre, and plenty of on-site parking.&nbsp;Floor 3 of the centre features an 18 foot long curved mural,&nbsp;Home Is Where the Heart Is.</p>
